1
00:00:59,199 --> 00:01:01,257
Yujin’s here?

2
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:04,320
Yeah.

3
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,540
You haven’t had dinner yet, right?
Wait a bit. Let’s go eat something good.

4
00:01:10,721 --> 00:01:11,908
Okay.

5
00:01:15,989 --> 00:01:18,952
Hyung, this…
it’s your birthday gift.

6
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:21,317
What…

7
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:34,391
This is expensive…

8
00:01:35,129 --> 00:01:38,744
How could a student afford something like this?

9
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:46,680
Don’t tell me…
you did that photoshoot to buy this?

10
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:49,572
Huh?
How did you know?

11
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:55,943
Yujin…
I don’t want a gift like this.

12
00:01:55,943 --> 00:01:59,036
Your feelings are enough.

13
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:05,117
No…
I didn’t force myself.

14
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:32,068
Stop it.
No—don’t come. Don’t wait for me.

15
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:47,705
Yujin…
wait. Just a second.

16
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,079
Hyung…

17
00:03:02,552 --> 00:03:04,790
Do you really have to go?

18
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,574
I…

19
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:18,561
I like you, hyung.
I’ve liked you for a long time.

20
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:29,326
Yujin…

21
00:03:30,301 --> 00:03:31,429
You…

22
00:03:32,449 --> 00:03:33,950
to me…

23
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:43,439
you’re my little brother.

24
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,148
I’m sorry…

25
00:04:01,757 --> 00:04:04,257
I’ll get going first.

26
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:07,764
Oh my—are you okay?
You didn’t hurt your hand, did you?

27
00:07:09,078 --> 00:07:11,613
Ah, I’m sorry…

28
00:07:12,225 --> 00:07:14,206
I’ll clean it up.

29
00:07:15,770 --> 00:07:19,756
No, it’s okay. I’ll do it.
Boss, just a moment.

30
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:23,736
Boss, you’ve been out of it all day.
Go inside and get some rest.

31
00:07:23,832 --> 00:07:25,944
You look really pale.

32
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:34,860
Sorry. I’ll go in for a minute.

33
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:03,224
I like you, hyung.
I’ve liked you for a long time.

34
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:39,038
You look like you didn’t sleep at all.

35
00:08:39,038 --> 00:08:41,819
You look terrible.

36
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,398
I’ve known you a long time.

37
00:08:47,874 --> 00:08:50,426
You… and Yujin too.

38
00:08:51,877 --> 00:08:57,035
I don’t know exactly how you feel.
But I know one thing.

39
00:08:58,478 --> 00:09:01,841
Whenever it’s about Yujin,
you’ve always been different.

40
00:09:01,841 --> 00:09:04,798
People don’t go that far for “just a little brother.”

41
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,270
I…

42
00:09:10,471 --> 00:09:12,211
Yujin…

43
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,813
I’m not supposed to feel that way.

44
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,365
Not supposed to?

45
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:27,299
I don’t know what he means to you either.

46
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,614
But…

47
00:09:28,614 --> 00:09:31,092
can you still say he’s “just your brother”?

48
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:39,240
I don’t know.

49
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,241
But…

50
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,518
I can’t say it’s not true anymore.

51
00:09:47,516 --> 00:09:49,706
Then that’s enough.

52
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:54,008
At least now you can’t pretend you don’t know.

53
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:04,247
You’re not the type
to take care of someone like that.

54
00:10:04,564 --> 00:10:09,158
But with him…
you always have been.

55
00:10:24,155 --> 00:10:26,563
Yujin, I need to talk to you.

56
00:10:46,016 --> 00:10:48,722
Yujin, I need to talk to you.

57
00:11:02,399 --> 00:11:03,359
Hyung…

58
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,955
I miss you.

59
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,522
I still…

60
00:11:13,522 --> 00:11:15,515
I can’t hear it yet.
